overview: The life and times of Dawn Davenport, showing her progression from bratty schoolgirl to crazed mass murderer - all of which stems from her parents' refusal to buy her cha-cha heels for Christmas.
tagline: Nice girls don't wear cha-cha heels.
cast: Divine|David Lochary|Mary Vivian Pearce|Mink Stole|Edith Massey
